snippet.title: Early Look At Mordor - Update 21 pre-Bullroarer - Lord of the Rings Online
snippet.description: Cordovan, QuartermasterU, DrOctothorpe, Severlin, Chris Pierson, and Tybur provide an early look at Update 21: Mordor, the day before our first preview on Bullroarer. Thank you for watching!
